	ANNULAR RING			0.100 mm
	COPPER TO HOLE		0.250 mm
	COPPER TO EDGE		0.500 mm
	HOLE TO HOLE			0.250 mm

11)	REFER TO IMPEDANCE TABLE FOR IMPEDANCE CONTROL REQUIREMENTS.

